speedy economic growth, saying that Eritrea is a young nation, and
the Eritrean people long for economic prosperity and stability.
</P>
<P>
The trip to Guangdong is the second leg of his Asian tour. He
said that he came to Guangdong for one special purpose: to learn
more about the province's experience in using foreign investment
to set up special economic zones, hoping that the two sides will
increase contact and exchanges to promote bilateral cooperation.
</P>
<P>
While in Guangdong, the president will see an exhibition on the
province's achievements in reform and opening up, and visit
Shenzhen and Dongguan as well as local businesses and urban
construction projects. 
