<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, April 5 (Xinhua) -- The 9th Asian Women's Volleyball
Championship will be held from September 21 to 25 in Baguio city,
a famous tourist site in the northern Philippines, officials said
here on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Kazuaki Yokoyama, Secretary-general and Managing Director of
the Asian Volleyball Confederation, presided over Saturday's
drawing for the preliminary round of the event.
</P>
