<HEADLINE> New EU Initiative for Renewing Syrian-Israeli </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, April 5 (Xinhua) -- The European Union (EU) has
proposed a new initiative for renewing the Middle East peace
talks on the Syrian-Israeli track under the principle of "full
withdrawal for full security."
</P>
<P>
