the principle of full withdrawal for full security. The approval
of the initiative will constitute a new start for renewing the
Syrian-Israeli negotiation.
</P>
<P>
Moratinos is currently in Dubai for participating in the
Arab-European dialogue forum that probes the potentials of
boosting the Arab-European cooperation in different fields.
