While in the women's sections, Estefania Juan won the 46-kg
category, Rebeca Sires notched up the title in the 50kg category
and Josefa Perez had the title in the 59-kg division for Spain.
</P>
<P>
Other four gold medals were split by Finland, Greece, Portugal
and Belgium. 
